    <div id="Peanut Butter Rice Krispie Treats">
      <h2>Peanut Butter Rice Krispie Treats</h2>

      <h3>Ingredients</h3>
      <p>
        <br />
        1/2 cup corn syrup <br />
        1/2 cup  brown sugar <br />
        1/2 cup peanut butter <br/>
        3 cups rice krispies
      </p>
      <h3>Instructions</h3>
      <p>
        1) Combine syrup and brown sugar in saucepan <br />
        2) Cook over moderate heat, stirring occasionally until mixture bubbles <br />
        3) Remove from heat <br />
        4) Stir in peanut butter <br />
        5) Add cereal and coconut or cushed nuts <br />
        6) Stir until coated
        7) Push evenly into bottom of 8x8 pan <br />
        8) Let stand in cool place until firm
      </p>
    </div>
  </body>
